---
title: Golden Grain-Stuffed Peppers with Sun-Dried Tomatoes and Zucchini
description: If stuffed peppers had a motto, it would be “Roast it, fill it, and rock ’n’ roll.” That’s because in the scheme of foods stuffed with other foods, peppers are relatively no-fuss and all about getting a little messy. These oven-roasted beauties are just that: they’re filled with a colorful mix of sun-dried tomatoes, zucchini, and fresh mozzarella, plus a special blend of four different grains that spills onto the plate.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/w13-r10-7cab189d.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/w13-r10-20de1ef7.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
cuisine: North America
